name: Organic Blue Dream Mandala Dance VII
description:
Part of a series of organic geometry while testing trapcode TAO normal map textures. [17-10-18] 
In celebration of the opening of legal recreational marijuana distribution stores in the province of Quebec. Served as VJLoops (available with alpha channel).| 1:1 | 640x640 | 500 Frames | 15 FPS.

This will become a series of #HEN200 because it is something I like sharing with you all and hopefully allowing you to later make some profit flipping it on 420 or something like that.
